author: Anonymous Beaker
title: autograding error
question: I finished my lab, but autograding report  did not show my grade.
instructor_answer:
Because your Piazza username does not match any name in the course I can't really tell for sure what happened here, but I do know that at least one student did this in their handin:
;;(@assignment labs/lab-02) 
Commenting out the assignment tag essentially disables the autograder.
